Package: manageR
Title: Shiny app to help freelancers
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Benjamin", "Louis", , "contact@benjaminlouis-stat.fr", c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The package {manageR} contains a dashboard shiny app that give tools to freelancers to help with day to day management. So far, the app allows to organise data about clients, billing addresses, quotes and invoices. Users are able to print personalised pdf of quotes and invoices based on saved data.
